      "writtenOn": "2020-05-05T20:10:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "What information off the backend texture would tell us this info? Remember this function will be used for updating backend textures that may not have been created inside of skia. We don\u0027t have it currently but if we had the usage flags on the vk info you could tell \"if\" the texture has the ability to be rendered to. But I would argue that is really what we want here. The only time I feel like we want to move it the color attachment layout is if we are newly creating a renderable backend texture. If someone told us to update the values in a generic renderable backend texture I feel like they most likely will be sampling that texture next.",
